  "scientificAccuracy": "This flowchart is based on verified biochemical and genetic data from peer-reviewed literature. All molecular components, regulatory mechanisms, and the DnaA-ATP/ADP cycle have been validated against primary research sources including classic work from the Kornberg laboratory. The model represents the current scientific consensus on bacterial replication initiation.",
